Manufacturer InformationTimberland is a renowned brand in the global market for fashion and the label was created in the year 1918 as an entity dealing in the manufacturing of shoes. Nathan Swartz is the founder of this distinguished brand, which has progressed by leaps and bounds to emerge as an impressive corporate giant in the world of brands, sustaining its lead in the fashion market. Nathan first worked as an apprentice in Massachusetts, he was a man of vision. It is this vision that is inculcated into the approaches of this organization that has helped in its development in every era. The brand name Timberland however, was established in the year 1973, with the introduction of the waterproof boots. In the 1990's Timberland extended its product line encompassing and array of fashion accessories under its brand umbrella which also included watches. One of the best things about watches developed by Timberland is their sophisticated yet, simpler technological options, offering various spectacular designs in both the digital and analogue forms. The contemporary design of Timberland watches can fit in with almost all styles in fashion, from attractive formal watches, glittering with elegance to sporty watches for casual wear and tough sports watches with water resistance and customized stainless steel and leather bands. Timberland watches not only provide comfort but make the ideal designer accessory piece.
